# OpenFOAM / wmake build artifacts
platforms/
**/lnInclude/
**/Make/linux*/
**/*.dep
**/*.o
**/*.so
**/*.a
**/*.log

# Editor / local tooling
.vscode/
.codex
.codex/
VS workspaces/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
._*

# OpenFOAM case runtime output
**/postProcessing/
**/processor*/
**/dynamicCode/
**/logs/
**/log.*
**/slurm-*.out
**/*.foam

# Time directories generated by runs
**/[1-9]*/
**/[1-9][0-9]*/
**/[1-9][0-9][0-9]*/
**/[0-9]*.[0-9]*/

# Mesh/zone helper files often generated during preprocessing
**/constant/polyMesh/*Zonesignore
